README for DiML-styles version 0.1c

These are XSL Stylesheets for the DiML XML DTD
(or to be honest they are planned to be).

The DiML DTD is a modularized XML schema for scientific
documents developed at the Humboldt University, Berlin.
For more information on DiML, see http://edoc.hu-berlin.de/diml/

For more information on DiML-styles, see http://thema.sourceforge.net/

Manifest
--------

README               this file
TODO                 planned features not yet implemented
module-CALStable/    styles for elements of module CALStable
module-citation/     styles for elements of module citation
